function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
	--Follower to Static
	sickFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(S_FOLLOWER_SICK)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(sickFollower) then 
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(sickFollower)
		Hydra.QActorEnableAI(sickFollower, false)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(sickFollower, ID_SICK, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(sickFollower, ID_SICK)
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(sickFollower, ANIM_PAIN)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(sickFollower)
		Hydra.ActorDeleteNPCClone(sickFollower, Hydra.ACDID_INVALID, false);
	end
	
end

function Start()

	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()

	--Healer Static NPC + Movement
	
	actorClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_HEAL_FLIES)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorClone) then	
		Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(actorClone)
		Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(actorClone, ANIM_CONFUSED)
		Hydra.QActorWait(actorClone, 0.5)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(CONVO_HEALER_02, id_Self, actorClone)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorClone, LOC_HEALER_FLIES_END, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorClone, LOC_HEALER_FLIES_END) 
		Hydra.QActorWait(actorClone, 0.3)

		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(actorClone, 0)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	
	--Guard Clone + Bark
	sickClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_SICK)
	guardClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_GUARD)
	VilClone_01 = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_VIL_01)
	VilClone_02 = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_VIL_02)
	healerClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_HEAL)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(guardClone) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(healerClone) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(VilClone_01) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(VilClone_02) then
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(VilClone_01)
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(VilClone_02)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(VilClone_01, ID_VIL_SICK_01, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(VilClone_02, ID_VIL_SICK_02, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceActor(VilClone_01, sickClone) 
		Hydra.QActorFaceActor(VilClone_02, sickClone) 
		Hydra.QActorFaceActor(guardClone, sickClone) 
		Hydra.QActorWait(guardClone, 1)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(CONVO_GUARD_01, id_Self, guardClone)
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(healerClone)
		Hydra.QActorWait(healerClone, 0.5)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(healerClone, LOC_HEALER_END, "NPC_RUN", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceActor(healerClone, sickClone) 
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(healerClone, ANIM_KNEEL)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(CONVO_HEALER_01, id_Self, healerClone)
		Hydra.QActorWait(healerClone, 1.5)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(healerClone)
	end
		
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(guardClone) then
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(guardClone, CONVO_GUARD_01)	
		Hydra.QActorWait(guardClone, 0.5)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(guardClone)
	end
	
	--Villager Controls
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(healerClone) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(VilClone_01) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(VilClone_02) then
		Hydra.QActorWait(healerClone, 1.5)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(healerClone)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(VilClone_01)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(VilClone_02)
	end

	Hydra.EventSendToActor("QST_SOULROT_01_THEATER", idSelf, idSelf)
	
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	--Clone Cleanup + Poison Blast
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(sickClone) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(guardClone) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(VilClone_01) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(VilClone_02) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(guardClone) then
		Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(sickClone, 5)
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(sickClone, FX_POISON_BLAST)
		Hydra.ActorDeleteNPCClone(sickClone, Hydra.ACDID_INVALID, false);
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(healerClone, 0)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(VilClone_01, 0)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(VilClone_02, 0)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(guardClone, 0)
	end
	
	Hydra.EventSend("QST_VGN_SOULROT_01")
	
end
